title: Y-3 Crinkle Twill Cargo Pants
body_html:
Y-3 CRINKLE TWILL CARGO PANTS

CARGO PANTS WITH TAFFETA LINING FROM Y-3.

The Y-3 CRINKLE TWILL CARGO PANTS combines a classic design with functional details for an unexpected style. The all-over print looks great in a loose silhouette. Lined with smooth taffeta on the inside.

title: Y-3 Workwear LS Shirt
body_html:
A UTILITARIAN, LONG SLEEVE, BUTTON-UP Y-3 SHIRT.

The Y-3 Workwear Long Sleeve Shirt is an exploration of functionality in the world of fashion. The loose silhouette has a classic look with buttons down the front and on the cuffs.

title: Y-3 Crepe Pocket T-Shirt
body_html:
A UTILITARIAN Y-3 TEE WITH ADJUSTABLE DETAILS.

The Y-3 Crepe Pocket Tee is an exploration of functionality in a fashion landscape. The relaxed silhouette is fabricated from lightweight crepe jersey material with a bungee-adjustable tie cord.

title: Y-3 Utility Cargo Pants
body_html:
FUNCTIONAL CARGO PANTS MADE FROM NATURALLY WRINKLED FABRIC.

The Y-3 UTILITY CARGO PANTS puts a fresh twist on a classic, functional design. The trousers are made from washed twill with a wrinkled, loose silhouette. Webbing tape, FIDLOCK® snap buckles, pockets, and metallic accents add a casual overall look.

title: Y-3 Crepe Jersey SS Pocket Tee
body_html:
Y-3 CREPE JERSEY SHORT SLEEVE POCKET TEE
A LOOSE Y-3 TEE WITH CREPE ACCENTS.
The Y-3 Crepe Jersey Short Sleeve Pocket Tee borrows from classic and functional approaches, then diverts from the expected. It's made of soft, lightweight cotton single jersey with crepe pockets as a contrast. The loose fit drapes casually with ease.

title: Y-3 Crinkle Nylon Blazer
body_html:
Y-3 CRINKLE NYLON BLAZER
A TAILORED Y-3 BLAZER.
The Y-3 Crinkle Nylon Blazer borrows from classic and functional design approaches, then diverts from the expected. The tailored silhouette drapes elegantly with a relaxed fit.

title: Y-3 Half-Zip Short Sleeve Tee
body_html:
A LOOSE Y-3 TEE WITH BRUSHSTROKE GRAPHICS.

The Y-3 Half-Zip Short Sleeve Tee is a harmonious balance between fashion and sport. The loose silhouette is crafted from premium cotton single jersey material with a shaped, ribbed collar. The Y-3 logo on the chest looks as if it was painted on with a wide brushstroke in a nod to archival Yohji Yamamoto pieces.

title: Y-3 Logo Knit Cardigan
body_html:
Y-3 LOGO KNIT CARDIGAN
A Y-3 CARDIGAN WITH BRUSHSTROKE GRAPHICS.
The Y-3 Logo Knit Cardigan is a harmonious balance between fashion and sport. The classic silhouette is crafted from soft, cosy knit material and has a relaxed fit. An engineered Y-3 graphic is done up in extra-fuzzy yarn.

title: Y-3 Graphic Logo French Terry Pants
body_html:
Y-3 PANTS WITH AN OVERSIZED BRUSHSTROKE GRAPHIC.

The Y-3 Graphic Logo French Terry Pants create a harmonious balance between fashion and sport. The relaxed silhouette hangs with a casual slouch for a soft, comfortable feel. A nod to archival Yohji Yamamoto pieces, the brushstroke graphic details take over the left leg.

title: Y-3 Team Jacket
body_html:
A COLLEGIATE-INSPIRED Y-3 JACKET WITH BRUSHSTROKE GRAPHICS.

The Y-3 Team Jacket is a harmonious balance between fashion and sport. A classic collegiate silhouette, it's crafted from 100% nylon ottoman-weave material and has a smooth taffeta lining. Lightweight PrimaLoft® insulation adds warmth. Brushstroke graphics nod to archival Yohji Yamamoto pieces.

title: Y-3 Shirt
body_html:
"SHIRT" is located where the two areas of adidas and Yohji Yamamoto clearly intersect.
Relaxed button down by Y-3.
The Y-3 Shirt sits at the clear crossroads of the two realms of adidas and Yohji Yamamoto.
A high-quality, heavyweight garment with a relaxed fit.
Loose-fit front with button closure, 59% cotton/33% nylon/8% spandex (plain weave), and heavy textured Y-3 logo.

title: Y-3 Superstar
body_html:
Y-3 SUPERSTAR
Y-3'S TAKE ON THE ADIDAS SUPERSTAR SHOES, INSPIRED BY TRADITIONAL SASHIKO STITCHING.
Arguably one of adidas' most celebrated trainers, the iconic Superstar Shoes get an update from Y-3. They're fabricated in premium nubuck and suede materials. In a nod to the Japanese technique of Sashiko stitching, the trainers have accentuated and tonal stitching around the eyestay, heel tab, midsole and the signature 3-Stripes, with all threads intentionally hanging loosely. The classic rubber shell toe stands out even more with thick embroidery where the original lines usually are.

title: Desert Boot
body_html:
Cultural cachet and design DNA: no shoe is quite like the Clarks Originals Desert Boot. Nathan Clark’s 1950 design was inspired by a rough boot from Cairo’s Old Bazaar, and its minimal, progressive style sparked a worldwide footwear revolution – worn by beatniks, mods, Britpop bands, and Jamaican rude boys, from Paris to Kingston, Tokyo to London. Every design detail today remains true to that first pioneering pair – here, the boot’s crafted, clean lines are enhanced with premium beeswax leather, finished with an unfussy lace fastening. The authentic, sustainably sourced crepe sole completes this distinctive silhouette. Instantly recognizable, forever iconic. A true original.
